'''Khan Bonfils''' was an English actor who portrayed [[Saesee Tiin]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']] (and in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']] via archive footage).

He died on [[January 5]], [[2015]] at 42 after collapsing during rehearsals for a theater production of [[Wikipedia:Dante Alighieri|Dante]]'s [[Wikipedia:Inferno (Dante)|''Inferno'']].<ref name="Death" />

